replies.txt_content:
Alorw 发表于 2018-8-18 09:47
ProxiedPlayer p = (ProxiedPlayer) sender
我原来是这样写的
ProxiedPlayer p;
p = (ProxiedPlayer) sender;

你需要检查一下才能转换：
if(sender instanceof ProxiedPlayer) {
    ProxiedPlayer p = (ProxiedPlayer) sender;
}复制代码

